266
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:56,480
You're suffering under your stupid master, aren't you?

267
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,350
Don't say it so soulfully!

268
00:15:57,350 --> 00:15:57,860
- All right, I will save you!
Don't say it so soulfully!

269
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:59,560
- All right, I will save you!

270
00:15:59,560 --> 00:15:59,810
What?!
- All right, I will save you!

271
00:15:59,810 --> 00:16:00,100
What?!

272
00:16:00,840 --> 00:16:01,580
See you 'round!

273
