290
00:16:52,750 --> 00:16:53,200
Yeah, I guess.

291
00:16:54,060 --> 00:16:56,630
It's the physical form of a precious memory...

292
00:16:58,540 --> 00:16:59,800
Am I wrong?

293
00:17:00,820 --> 00:17:02,080
I don't know...

294
00:17:02,610 --> 00:17:04,000
Yeah, I guess you're right.

295
00:17:06,190 --> 00:17:07,310
That ruined the mood!

296
00:17:07,310 --> 00:17:08,110
- Shut up!
That ruined the mood!

297
00:17:08,110 --> 00:17:08,680
- Shut up!

298
