299
00:17:14,550 --> 00:17:17,630
You're hungry, are you not?

300
00:17:26,580 --> 00:17:29,000
Tohno-san is amazing, isn't she?

301
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:32,830
Not only is she good at her studies, but she's good at sewing, too.

302
00:17:32,830 --> 00:17:35,900
So, where are we headed?

303
00:17:35,900 --> 00:17:37,980
A place where lots of people gather.

304
00:17:37,980 --> 00:17:42,300
If you put on your puppet show there, lots of people should gather.

305
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:45,470
It's Mom.

306
00:17:45,900 --> 00:17:48,700
What sort of work does Haruko do?

307
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:49,850
It's a secret.

308
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:52,530
I wonder if she went to say a prayer at the shrine.

309
00:17:52,530 --> 00:17:53,260
The shrine?

310
00:17:53,260 --> 00:17:55,190
Yeah. Where we're headed now.

311
00:17:57,230 --> 00:17:59,090
Hey, there's no one here!

312
00:17:59,550 --> 00:18:01,650
