318
00:18:19,820 --> 00:18:21,480
Let's play hide-and-seek!

319
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:22,340
What?!

320
00:18:22,590 --> 00:18:25,390
I want to play hide-and-seek with you, Yukito-san.

321
00:18:25,390 --> 00:18:27,250
How old are we, anyway?

322
00:18:27,530 --> 00:18:29,800
Then... Then let's catch bugs.

323
00:18:31,120 --> 00:18:32,210
Gao!

324
00:18:40,330 --> 00:18:42,160
Oh, fish!

325
00:18:42,210 --> 00:18:43,520
I want to catch fish.

326
00:18:45,170 --> 00:18:46,980
You don't care what it is, do you?

327
00:18:47,660 --> 00:18:50,740
It's summer vacation, so I want to play as much as I can.

328
00:18:55,170 --> 00:18:56,030
Hey, Misuzu!

329
00:18:58,450 --> 00:19:01,730
